user_prompt_template:
Analyze this job posting against the user profile and return a JSON response.

Job Details:
Title: {job_title}
Company: {job_company}
Location: {job_location}
Description: {job_description}
Requirements: {job_requirements}

User Profile:
Skills: {user_skills}
Experience: {user_experience_years} years
Education: {user_education}
Preferred Roles: {user_preferred_roles}
Preferred Locations: {user_preferred_locations}

Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "role_classification": "string (e.g., DevOps, Cloud Engineer, SRE, Research Associate, PhD Position, Postdoc, etc.)",
  "match_score": number (0-100),
  "extracted_skills": ["skill1", "skill2"],
  "missing_skills": ["skill1", "skill2"],
  "summary": "string (2-3 sentences)",
  "reasoning": "string (why this score, what matches, what's missing)",
  "should_alert": boolean (true if match_score >= 75)
}
